### Welcome to BoaRx.
These are the humble beginnings of some utility applications for Internal Medicine physicians.  I envision create apps for calculations and note templates.  Perhaps checklists would be helpfule.

### Authors and Contributors
Right now it's just @ralflukner.  Contact me to join this project or for more information.
